               <msContents>
                  <summary>Image of Kiros, መልክዐ፡ ኪሮስ፡; Acts of Gäbrä Mänfäs Qǝddus, ገድለ፡ ገብረ፡ መንፈስ፡ ቅዱስ፡, Acts of Abba Kiros, ገድለ፡ ኪሮስ።</summary>
                     <textLang mainLang="gez">Gǝ‘ǝz</textLang>
                 <msItem xml:id="ms_i1"><locus from="1r" to="1v" facs="002">Fols 1r–1v</locus><title type="incomplete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT2851RepCh133">Malkǝʾ-hymn to St
                                                  Kiros</title><note>fragment</note></msItem>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i2"><locus from="2r" to="58r" facs="003">Fols 2r–58r</locus><title>Acts of Gäbrä Mänfäs Qǝddus, Gädlä Gäbrä Mänfäs Qǝddus, <foreign xml:lang="gez">ገድለ፡ ገብረ፡ መንፈስ፡ ቅዱስ፡</foreign></title>
                    <msItem xml:id="ms_i2.1"><locus from="2r" to="41r" facs="003">Fols 2r–41r</locus><title type="incomplete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT1451GadlaG">Gadla Gabra Manfas
                                                  Qǝddus (general record)</title><note>incomplete at the beginning</note></msItem>
                    <msItem xml:id="ms_i2.2"><locus from="41r" to="58r" facs="042">Fols 41r–58r</locus><title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT3977Taammer">Taʾammǝra Gabra
                                                  Manfas Qǝddus</title>
                    <note>Thirteen miracles</note>
                    <incipit xml:lang="gez">
                      በስመ: አብ: ወወልድ:<gap reason="omitted"/>ንጽሕፍ: ዜና: ገድሉ: ተአምሪሁ: ነፍሱ: ወሥጋሁ:<gap reason="omitted"/>
                    </incipit>
                  </msItem>
                  </msItem>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i3"><locus from="59r" to="85v" facs="060">Fols 59r–85v</locus><title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT5134KirosGeneral">Gadla Kiros
                                                  (general record)</title>
                  <incipit xml:lang="gez">
                    በስመ: አብ: ወወልድ:<gap reason="omitted"/> ንቀድም: በረድኤተ: እግዚአብሔር: ገድል: ዘቅዱስ: ወብፁዕ: አባ: ኪሮስ: ጸሎቱ: ወበረከቱ: የሀሉ: ምስለ: ገብሩ: [lacuna] ለዓለመ: ዓለም: አሜን።
                  </incipit>
                </msItem>
               </msContents>
